                          Average deaths prevented per region

                 Business questions
What is the average deaths prevented per region? 

                     Query
SELECT
  region,
  ROUND(AVG(deaths_prevented),2)AVG_deaths_prevented
FROM cancer_data
GROUP by region
ORDER BY AVG_deaths_prevented DESC;

Insight
This helps compare performance efficiency of each region.

Recommendation
Regions with low averages deaths prevented may need better implementation, not just more funding.
